---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Getting Started with FuryStack">
  <main id="main-content" class="page-main">
    <div class="page-inner">
      <h1>Getting Started</h1>
      <div class="page-content">
        <p class="lead">
          FuryStack is a flexible, end-to-end TypeScript framework for building complex services.
          Choose the path that fits your needs.
        </p>

        <div class="cards">
          <a href="/getting-started/boilerplate/" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="28"
                height="28"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path>
                <path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="6" x2="12" y2="14"></line>
                <line x1="8" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Use the Boilerplate</h2>
            <p>
              Clone a ready-made template repository with authentication, a REST API, and a Shades
              frontend &mdash; all wired up and ready to hack on.
            </p>
            <span class="card-cta">Get started &rarr;</span>
          </a>

          <a href="/getting-started/from-scratch/" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="28"
                height="28"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Build from Scratch</h2>
            <p>
              Set up a Yarn monorepo step by step: shared models, a FuryStack backend, and a Shades
              frontend &mdash; understanding every piece along the way.
            </p>
            <span class="card-cta">Start building &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <hr />

        <h2>Next steps</h2>
        <p>
          Once you have a project running, dive deeper into individual FuryStack concepts. Each
          guide below is kept up to date with the latest API.
        </p>
        <ul class="next-steps">
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started/inject/">Dependency Injection</a>
            &mdash; <code>defineService</code>, tokens, lifetimes, and disposable scopes
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started/data-stores/">Data Stores</a>
            &mdash; <code>defineStore</code> with in-memory, filesystem, MongoDB, Redis, or SQL backends
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started/repository/">Repository</a>
            &mdash; DataSets with authorization, modifiers, and change events
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started/rest/">REST</a>
            &mdash; type-safe API contracts shared between server and client
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started/data-validation/">Data Validation</a>
            &mdash; JSON Schema validation for endpoint payloads
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-main {
    flex-grow: 1;
    padding: calc(64px + 48px) 5vw 80px;
    background: #fff;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .page-main {
      background: var(--color-darkmode);
    }
  }

  .page-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-inner h1 {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 3.6rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-inner h1 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
    }
  }

  .page-content {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-body);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .page-content {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-darkgrey);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .lead {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    }
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 650px) {
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition:
      transform 0.25s ease,
      box-shadow 0.25s ease,
      border-color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .card {
      background: var(--color-darkmode-l04);
      border-color: var(--color-darkmode-border);
    }
    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: var(--color-accent);
    }
  }

  .card-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .card-icon {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    }
  }

  .card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-midgrey);
    margin: 0 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    }
  }

  .card-cta {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .page-content h2 {
    margin-top: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .next-steps {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }
  .next-steps li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .next-steps code {
    font-size: 0.88em;
  }
</style>
